root: ^Fantastic view of the green California hills and coastline!
^Strong, cool breezes and that salty sweet smell of the waves crashing!
^Several seagull attacks on the beach all year round, with a 75 year long power struggle between the gulls and the Pismo coast guard vying for control of the beach territory!
^What more could you want from a place like this!?
^Do you want some stuff? Here ya go
